---
import "../../styles/global.css";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>Xiaomi Humanoid - Xi Lin</title>
  </head>
  <body class="bg-white text-gray-900">
    <main class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-16 sm:px-10">
      <a href="/" class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-900">Back to home</a>
      <p class="mt-6 text-sm font-mono text-blue-600">Xiaomi Robotics | Robotics Engineer Intern</p>
      <h1 class="mt-3 text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-5xl">Humanoid Motion Retargeting and Skill Simulation</h1>
      <p class="mt-5 max-w-4xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600">
        This experience focused on humanoid robot hardware configuration optimization and simulation systems. I converted factory assembly videos into SMPL trajectories, retargeted complex human motions to humanoids with PHC, and built simulation and low-level policy training loops for assembly-style and payload-related tasks.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-10 grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-[1.1fr_0.9fr]">
        <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-[28px] border border-gray-200 bg-black">
          <video controls playsinline class="w-full">
            <source src="/assets/projects/xiaomi-retargeting-demo.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
          </video>
        </div>
        <section class="rounded-[28px] border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-6">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">Program Core</h2>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-gray-600">
            <li>Converted factory assembly videos into SMPL trajectories and retargeted complex human motions to humanoids with PHC, creating a reusable motion dataset for downstream training.</li>
            <li>Built high-fidelity simulation environments in Unitree RL Gym and trained low-level tracking policies for dexterous assembly-style robot behaviors.</li>
            <li>Benchmarked ASAP and related pipelines in a unified physics stack for tasks such as payload walking, while building automated evaluation tooling for sim-to-real iteration.</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="mt-5 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            {["WBC", "Retargeting", "RL", "sim2sim", "SMPL", "Unitree RL Gym"].map((item) => (
              <span class="rounded-full border border-gray-300 bg-white px-3 py-1.5 text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">
                {item}
              </span>
            ))}
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>

      <section class="mt-10 rounded-[28px] border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 sm:p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Detailed Demo Frames</h2>
        <div class="mt-6 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
          <article class="rounded-3xl border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-4">
            <video controls playsinline class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-black">
              <source src="/assets/projects/xiaomi-tightening-demo.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
            </video>
            <img src="/assets/projects/xiaomi-tightening-frame.png" alt="Tightening operation frame" class="mt-4 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200" />
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-600">Demo: tightening operations with torque below 20 Nm, used to validate low-level tracking and task-conditioned behavior quality.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="rounded-3xl border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-4">
            <video controls playsinline class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-black">
              <source src="/assets/projects/xiaomi-finetune-demo.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
            </video>
            <img src="/assets/projects/xiaomi-guide-config.png" alt="Guide config design" class="mt-4 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200" />
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-600">Guide-config design and RL finetuning were used to stabilize behavior quality and adapt the motion policies to task-specific constraints.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="rounded-3xl border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-4">
            <video controls playsinline class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-black">
              <source src="/assets/projects/xiaomi-sim2sim-demo.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
            </video>
            <img src="/assets/projects/xiaomi-sim2sim-frame.png" alt="Sim2sim validation frame" class="mt-4 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200" />
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-600">Sim2sim evaluation was used to benchmark behavior transfer quality and support iterative comparison across different control stacks.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="rounded-3xl border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-4">
            <img src="/assets/projects/xiaomi-overview.png" alt="Xiaomi retargeting overview" class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200" />
            <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-600">This stage gave me direct experience with retargeting, whole-body control, reinforcement learning, and simulation-heavy engineering for practical humanoid behaviors.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
